{
  "texts": [
    "It also provides references for more sophisticated results.",
    "I want to mention existing short introduction to PAC-Bayes bounds, like the ones by McAllester (2013) and van Erven (2014) and the nice introductory slides of Fleuret (2011).",
    "They are very informative, and I recommend the reader to check them.",
    "However, they are focused on empirical bounds only.",
    "There are also surveys on PAC-Bayes bounds, such as Chopin et al. (2015, Section 5) or Guedj (2019)."
  ]
}